id: hac-4s9j
title: Maintain homeassistant-cli as a secure agent-optimized product
description: "Durable product umbrella for roadmap, repository ownership, quality, security, releases, and Home Assistant API evolution."
type: Epic
status: open
priority: 1
tags[5]: agents,home-assistant,maintenance,product,roadmap
created_at: "2026-07-16T17:07:03.007Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-16T17:07:25.250Z"
deadline: "2027-01-16T17:07:03.007Z"
assignee: unbraind
author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 10000
acceptance_criteria: "All active delivery work is linked beneath this umbrella; repository files and docs have baseline PM ownership; security, quality, release, and API evolution work has detailed child items; PM validation has no unowned repository paths"
goal: best-agent-home-assistant-cli
objective: secure-complete-intuitive-home-assistant-automation
value: Provide reliable Home Assistant control and discovery for agents and operators.
impact: Creates durable governance and ownership for all future repository work.
outcome: "A continuously maintained, secure, well-tested CLI with explicit roadmap lineage."
why_now: The repository is being initialized into PM and needs a canonical non-temporary owner for its pre-existing artifacts.
reviewer: unbraind
risk: medium
confidence: 95
sprint: product-roadmap
release: continuous
dependencies[1]{id,kind,created_at,author,source_kind}:
  hac-gpm3,related,"2026-07-16T17:07:03.007Z",codex-root,null
comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:07:03.007Z",codex-root,This umbrella owns baseline artifacts; active remediation remains in its dedicated child epic.
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:07:03.007Z",codex-root,Do not place this durable umbrella in progress unless its own metadata or ownership model is actively changing.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T17:07:03.007Z",codex-root,Repository initialization needs a durable product owner for legacy files; linking them to a temporary remediation issue creates misleading lineage.
