body: "## Product goal\\n\\nKeep the Home Assistant CLI broad, safe, token-efficient, reproducible, and easy for agents and humans to operate. This permanent umbrella owns the pre-existing repository baseline; concrete delivery happens in child epics, features, issues, stories, chores, and tasks."
